            }
        },
        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "But is it really a breaking change? If the user of the API is expecting `ArrayOf(Integer)`, they would have encountered issues if `{details: true}` was passed and they expected each element to be an integer. So, if we remove the constraint of integer array, I think it should not break this behaviour.\r\n\r\nI believe it should be a fix rather than a breaking change.\r\n\r\nPlease let me know if I am wrong.",
            "created_at": "2023-01-17T18:02:25Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/21719#issuecomment-1385820399",
            "id": 1385820399,
            "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/neovim/neovim/issues/21719",
            "node_id": "IC_kwDOAPphoM5SmfDv",
            "performed_via_github_app": null,
