        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "The problem is it might cause breaking changes in API clients which generate statically typed wrappers around the RPC functionality. Not sure it strictly happens for any in use client in the specific case of `ArrayOf(Number)` to `Array`, but strictly speaking it is a breaking change.",
            "created_at": "2023-01-17T18:07:21Z",
