        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Should I go ahead with creating a new function? Please let me know if these should be the correct checkpoints.\r\n- Create new function\r\n- Add similar test cases with change in type\r\n- Put deprecated tag on the previous function `FUNC_API_DECPRECATED_SINCE`\r\n\r\nAlso how does the `FUNC_API_SINCE` number change?",
