        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Should I go ahead with creating a new function?\r\n\r\nNo, not yet at least. IMO we should do the \"breaking\" change here. But we don't have a way to tell `version_spec.lua` about exceptional cases like this.",
